About this hotel

Off Highway 5, this unpretentious hotel is a mile from California State Railroad Museum, 2 miles from Old Sacramento State Historic Park and 3 miles from the California State Capitol.

Check-in time: 3:00 PM
Check-out time: 11:00 AM

    About this hotel

    Off Highway 5, this unpretentious hotel is a mile from California State Railroad Museum, 2 miles from Old Sacramento State Historic Park and 3 miles from the California State Capitol. …

    The airy rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minifridges, plus microwaves and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms add pool or garden views.

    Free breakfast is served in a casual dining area. Other amenities include an outdoor pool and a hot tub.
